{"id":38108,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":10,"day":16}],"page":"14","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园(第10期)","column":"图画故事","genre":"文学作品","count":"134","ytitle":"","mtitle":"爱国的华儿","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>子微</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入1号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1938\\10\\38ag140901.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(一)华儿是个很爱国的孩子，他每天把糖果钱节省下来，预备将来捐助政府。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入1号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1938\\10\\38ag140902.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(二)积了几个月，他已经积得很多的钱了。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入1号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1938\\10\\38ag140903.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(三)他叫仆人阿福挑到中央银行去，请他们转交给政府。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入1号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1938\\10\\38ag140904.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(四)政府把许多爱国儿童的钱，凑起来造成飞机，去打敌人，这飞机就呌做“华儿号”。</FONT>"}]}